             was indicted for <rs id="t18220220-119-off645" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220220-119-off645" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220220-119-off645" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18220220-119-cd646" type="crimeDate">28th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220220-119-off645 t18220220-119-cd646"></join>, one pair of boots, value 3 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18220220-119-victim1181" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Bishop
                  <interp inst="t18220220-119-victim1181" type="surname" value="Bishop"></interp>
